Invocation Name: python story
des:
Listen to an interactive spooky story with sound effects and prompts. When you open the skill, Alexa asks for character names and other information to fill in the blanks.
A spooky story on the Python Tribe from Unofficial O' Rielly, are you part of this tribe and the sacrifice of a fair maiden to the sacred gaint python you name?, maybe this is a pure society, where criminals are fed to sacred animals, for her crimes?
Get ready for laughs and giggles as your audience fills in the blanks and listens their customized story.
